Module kivakit.interfaces
Package com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.collection

Interface Sized

All Superinterfaces:
Emptiness
All Known Subinterfaces:
Addable<Value>, Appendable<Value>, Indexable<Value>, Prependable<Value>, Sectionable<Value,Section>, SpaceLimited, WriteIndexable<Value>
public interface Sized extends Emptiness
An object (usually some sort of collection or store of values) which has a size(). The object can be isEmpty() if the size is zero or Emptiness.isNonEmpty() if the size is non-zero.
